To solve the `indepFun_rewardByCount_Iic` problem, we need to prove that `rewardByCount A R a (n + 1)` is independent of the function `fun ω i => rewardByCount A R a (↑i) ω` with respect to the measure `P.prod (Bandit.streamMeasure ν)`.

