We need to prove the lemma `indepFun_rewardByCount_Iic` which states that `rewardByCount A R a (n + 1)` is independent of the function `fun ω i => rewardByCount A R a (↑i) ω` with respect to the probability measure `P.prod (Bandit.streamMeasure ν)`.

